## 4. Shapes — corner radius, borders

### 4.1. Corner radius

<Product-specific. Стандартные диапазоны:>
- Buttons / inputs / cards: X-Xpx
- Modals / large containers: X-Xpx
- Avatars: <circular / rounded>
